SUMMARY:UN Tech Over
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260622T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260622T173000
DESCRIPTION:The UN Tech Over brings people together to work on real UN challenges and build practical solutions through Hack-A-Thon, Edit-A-Thon, and Maintain-A-Thon activities.\nRSVP: https://www.unopensource.org/agenda
LOCATION:New York, NY
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:evt-2026-001@osweekplus.nyc
SUMMARY:UN Tech Over Hack-A-Thon, Edit-A-Thon, and Maintain-A-Thon
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260622T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260622T180000
DESCRIPTION:Imported from the DPGA UN Open Source Week schedule. See https://hackmd.io/@dpga/Sk05Nc21Me#UN-Tech-Over-%E2%80%94-Monday%2C-22-June for details.\nRSVP: https://hackmd.io/@dpga/Sk05Nc21Me#UN-Tech-Over-%E2%80%94-Monday%2C-22-June
