SUMMARY:High-Level Discussion: Open Source for Digital Development
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260623T111500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260623T120000
DESCRIPTION:The opening ministerial panel will reflect on how openness can strengthen international digital cooperation and bridge divides across countries and regions. Ministers will discuss how shared standards, open technologies, and collaborative governance approaches can enable more inclusive global digital ecosystems. The session will identify opportunities for cross-border partnerships that leverage openness to advance collective digital progress\nRSVP: https://www.unopensource.org/agenda
